items.description: Red tomato sauce with glossy surface, coating thin, light-brown spaghetti strands, forming a mound in the center of the plate
Yellowish-green, flaky, irregularly shaped pieces, likely herbs or spices, scattered among the meat and sauce, primarily in the center-right area
Dark brown, rough-textured, irregularly shaped chunks of meat, scattered atop the spaghetti, positioned at the top, center, and right side of the dish
